obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line 1
  line `THE MULTIMODAL TRANSPORTATION OF GOODS ACT, 1993`
  line __________
  line `ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS`
  line ________
  line `CHAPTER I`
  line `P RELIMINARY`
  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `1. Short title, extent and commencement.`
  line `2. Definitions.`
  line `CHAPTER II`
  line `R EGULATION OF MULTIMODAL TRANSPORTATION`
  line `3. No person to carry on business without registration.`
  line `4. Registration for multimodal transportation.`
  line `5. Cancellation of registration.`
  line `6. Appeal.`
  line `CHAPTER III`
  line `M ULTIMODAL TRANSPORT DOCUMENT`
  line `7. Issue of multimodal transport document.`
  line `8. Multimodal transport document to be regarded as document of title.`
  line `9. Contents of multimodal transport document.`
  line `10. Reservation in the multimodal transport document.`
  line `11. Evidentiary effect of the multimodal transport document.`
  line `12. Responsibility of the consignor.`
  line `CHAPTER IV`
  line `R ESPONSIBILITIES AND LIABILITIES OF THE MULTIMODAL TRANSPORT OPERATOR`
  line `13. Basis of liability of multimodal transport operator.`
  line `14. Limits of liability when the nature and value of the consignment have not been declared and stage`
  line `of transport where loss or damage occurred is not known.`
  line `15. Limits of liability when the nature and value of the consignment have not been declared and stage`
  line `of transport where loss or damage occurred is known.`
  line `16. Liability of the multimodal transport operator in case of delay in delivery of goods under certain`
  line circumstances.
  line `17. Assessment of compensation.`
  line `18. Loss of right of multimodal transport operator to limit liability.`
  line `19. Limit of liability of multimodal transport operator for total loss of goods.`
  line `20. Notice of loss of or damage to goods.`
  line `20A. Period of responsibility.`
  line `CHAPTER V`
  line `M ISCELLANEOUS`
  line `21. Special provision for dangerous goods.`
  line `22. Right of multimodal transport operator to have lien on goods and documents.`
  line `23. General average.`
  line `24. Limitation on action.`
  line `25. Jurisdiction for instituting action.`
